## Engineering Plan for the Client-Side React Demo App\
\
### Recommended Stack\
\
- __React 18+__\
- __TypeScript__\
- __Vite__\
- __React Router__\
- __Tailwind CSS__ or CSS modules for high-quality UI\
- __Lucide React__ for icons\
- __Local mock data__ in TypeScript files\
- Optional: browser `localStorage` for demo persistence\
- Static deployment to Render as a static site\
